Class SCUIState

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.sterlingcommerce.ui.web.framework.state.SCUIState

  • public class SCUIState
extends java.lang.Object
    Bean class which holds information about the state of a unique component for a user
    A component is uniquely identified using the combination of componentId, screenId and applicationId statikonda
